1.title: Overview
1.content: Welcome to the Financial Engineering Resource Hub ‚Äì a collection of technical documentation for engineers working on financial systems at Fake Company, Inc., with a primary focus on our Invoicing Platform Service (IPS) and related billing infrastructure. This site demonstrates how to document complex financial systems, onboard new engineers, and maintain operational knowledge for business-critical services.
